high_descs: Turn right, go to the door, turn right, go to the table.
Pick up the egg on the table.
Turn right, bring the egg to the sink on the right.
Wash the egg in the sink with water.
Turn around, bring the egg to the recycling bin to the left of the counter.
Put the cleaned egg in the recycling bin.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the table.
Pick up the egg that's in front of you.
Turn right and walk until you're even with the sink on your right then when you get to it turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the egg in the sink then pick it back up and turn off the faucet.
Turn right and walk to the microwave then turn right and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to he green garbage.
Put the egg in the garbage.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean egg in the garbage.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the table to the left near the door.
Pick up the egg.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Wash the egg in the sink.
Turn around and hang left to the green trash can.
Put the egg in the trash.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed egg in the trash.

high_descs: Turn right, walk towards the door, and then turn right towards the table.
Pick up the egg on the table.
Turn right and walk towards the oven, and then turn right towards the sink.
Place the egg in the sink, wash the egg, and pick up the egg.
Turn right, walk towards the fridge, and turn right towards the recycling bin.
Place the cleaned egg inside the bin.

high_descs: Turn to the right and move towards the brown door then turn right again and face the table.
Pick up the egg from the left corner of the table furthest away from you.
Turn right and move towards the oven then turn right again and move in front of the sink.
Place the egg in the sink, turn on the water to rinse the egg, then pick up the egg.
Turn right and move to the microwave, turn right again and move to the edge of the counter in front of the green recycling bin.
Place the egg in the recycling bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed egg into a recycling bin.
